This library provides the following arguments.
    --daemon      # Logs to the CLI.  If you don't specify a handler this is
                  # default.

    --pid_file    # Logs all messages debug and below.

EXAMPLE:
    import fram
    import fram_daemon

    def main(framework):
        LOGGER.debug("example debug")
        LOGGER.info("example info")
        LOGGER.warning("example warning")
        LOGGER.error("example error")

    if __name__ == "__main__":
        fram.run(func=main)
